parameters:
\nw[Kuno]The thief got a ride, but she didn't get
protected?

\nw[Nonna]Well... she was originally a mercenary and it
seems like she fought against other mercenary
groups and lost, causing her own group to disband.

\nw[Nonna]So she's saying that if there's a mercenary group,
she wants to join.
\nw[Kuno]The mercenary group... we were three people...

\nw[Kuno]...I see, so we joined a mercenary group, for the
time being.

\nw[Nonna]It seems like she didn't realize that the person
who was there with her was also captured. It seems
like they were carried away when their group lost
and they were injured.

\nw[Nonna]Um... it seems like this child was being embraced
since her mercenary days, so she didn't realize it
because it was a normal thing for her.

\nw[Nonna]The thief said that this child was a sex slave, so
there's no doubt that the purpose of the
confinement was for that.

\nw[Nonna]I can't just leave her alone, as she seems like
she might be deceived by someone if we leave
things as they are.

\nw[Kuno]I understand the situation... So, are you going to
take me with you?

\nw[Nonna]Yes, let's go back. Our base... to the newly
joined mercenary group.
